"title": "3218: Holy Spirit, and praise",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3218: holy spirit, and praise",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit inspires believers to extol, worship and thank God. His aim is to glorify the Father and the Son.</p>\n<h2>The promise that the Holy Spirit will bring praise</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">ISA 61:1–61:3</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit inspires praise</h2>\n<h3>True praise must be inspired by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:23-John4:24\">JHN 4:23–4:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:3\">PHP 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit prompts praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:1-2Sam23:2\">2SA 23:1–23:2</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:67-Luke1:68\">LUK 1:67–1:68</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:27-Luke2:28\">LUK 2:27–2:28</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a> <em>The Spirit prompts Jesus Christ to praise the Father.</em></p>\n<h2>Evidence of the Holy Spirit's work inspires praise</h2>\n<h3>The Spirit's convicting work inspires praise</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:24-1Cor14:25\">1CO 14:24–14:25</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit's converting work inspires praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:15-Acts11:18\">ACT 11:15–11:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit activates the church's praise</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18-Eph5:20\">EPH 5:18–5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44-Acts10:46\">ACT 10:44–10:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16-Col3:17\">COL 3:16–3:17</a></p>",
